{"tid":2079862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登: 1m=1000","createTime":"2020-06-26T05:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T01:05:31.000Z","uid":99700,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4c103f090517effecfbb18a703bfbe8bfa50c480","tid":2079862,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"拜登離譜失言 直說美國已超過1.2億人死於武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國民主黨總統參選人拜登（Joe Biden）25日在賓夕法尼亞州的競選活動中離譜失言，直說現在美國已有超過1.2億人（120 million）死於武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，按照約翰&middot;霍普金斯大學統計的數據來看，美國截至25日為止共有12萬2000多人因武漢肺炎病逝，拜登的失言等於是在這個數字上加3個0。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3209517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3209517&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Sn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d1e313a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3209517&h=a24bb35d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3209517</a>"},{"pid":"81ce3c848b087f4217fa440deb3d8997c19bff62","tid":2079862,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:33:23.000Z","msg":"唔小心講左真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b288beb2a8d1c36445c5467be34e8739594a8c39","tid":2079862,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"老過侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63541f1cbf49fe4f0dd5949080798cffde46f808","tid":2079862,"uid":114754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b36cf9124bc3f6858